dataset.title: A review of Australian long-horned caddisflies in the Oecetis pechana-group (Trichoptera: Leptoceridae), with descriptions of thirteen new species

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Wells, Alice (2006): A review of Australian long-horned caddisflies in the Oecetis pechana-group (Trichoptera: Leptoceridae), with descriptions of thirteen new species. Memoirs of Museum Victoria 63 (2): 107-128, DOI: 10.24199/j.mmv.2006.63.13, URL: https://museumsvictoria.com.au/collections-research/journals/memoirs-of-museum-victoria/volume-63-issue-2-2006/pages-107-128/
